data.title: Darlington City Council Regular Meeting
data.meta_description: Darlington City Council meeting - 1st Tuesday of the month at 6 pm at Town Hall. Access agendas/minutes and watch online.
data.meta_site_name: The City of Darlington, South Carolina
data.text:
Darlington City Council Meeting: City Council meets @ 6 p.m. on the first Tuesday of the month except when Holidays fall and schedule is amended.

Dates for 2024 are: January 2, February 6, March 5, April 9, May 7, June 4, July 9, August 6 (Rescheduled), September 3, October 1, November 12, December 3.

Watch the meeting live at City of Darlington, SC, Government | Darlington SC | Facebook.

You can find the agenda posted online by noon Monday prior to the meeting at https://www.cityofdarlington.com/city-council-agendas-meeting-minutes/.
